* Wed Jul 01 2026 RootGPT <166707820+RootGPT-YouTube@users.noreply.github.com> 0.9.0-1
- 0.9-beta.
- YouTube RSS: follow channels via their public RSS feeds (no API key, no quota);
  add by channel/video URL; import/export subscription lists and full-backup
  archives; Home grid of channels with avatars and unseen-video badges, with a
  long-press menu and multi-select (mark seen / delete). Playback opens in the
  system browser (in-app embedding not supported by the device browser engine).
- Removed the IPTV feature (broadcasters block out-of-app streaming).
- libVLC audio now follows the device media volume.

